OL,5, Batteries for e-bikes should be as     
OL,6, tightly regulated as fireworks, heavy  
OL,7, machinery or medical devices because of
OL,8, the fire-risk they pose, a charity has 
OL,9, said.                                  
OL,11,FIn June, a woman and two children died 
OL,12,Fin a fire linked to an e-bike battery. 
OL,14,FCurrently, manufacturers can           
OL,15,Fself-declare that e-bike and e-scooter 
OL,16,Fbatteries meet safety standards.       
OL,18,FBut campaigners Electrical Safety First
OL,19,Fsays these batteries should instead    
OL,20,Fneed third-party approval before sale. 
